{"tid":1850851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得武漢肺炎其實係人禍唔係天災","createTime":"2020-01-29T17:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T18:35:53.000Z","uid":140770,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0ca09a80dbe81c3ffc5a0338d716a0192a7584","tid":1850851,"uid":140770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:56:17.000Z","msg":"因為係武漢p4實驗室洩漏  所以特登搵網軍利用大量食老鼠蝌蚪蝙蝠視頻黎轉移視線<br />\n美國三次提出派出專家去支那協助抗疫都被支那拒絕  就係因為怕被發現<br />\n同埋支那一直拒絕公開病毒基因族譜就係怕被人發現隻武漢肺炎係武漢p4實驗室人工合成嘅<br />\n<br />\n結論：今次武漢肺炎有機會係支那原本想整生化武器 點知自己柒咗 喺武漢洩漏咗出嚟 搞到全世界都係病毒 <br />\n<br />\n大家小心d啦 記得戴口罩啊"},{"pid":"366f79123829118e07f7c26eda85e09679a80120","tid":1850851,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:56:56.000Z","msg":"Xiangguo Qiu"},{"pid":"5ff88f198fd6536a86ba808b267df54366d9e6fe","tid":1850851,"uid":321618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:57:22.000Z","msg":"好似啱啱睇左個差唔多樣嘅post<br />\n<br />\n醫護手足 點可以因為一場本可以封關避免嘅病毒而賭上生命<br />\n我地仲未光復到香港啊..<br />\nbtw p牌求推一推... <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥  借刀殺人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850782</a>"},{"pid":"d7887971624c1803f19ddbb223f9249506b255fd","tid":1850851,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家已經係獨立最佳時機，你，仲等緊啲咩<br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52579a29d63de6c90c9779b642dbac8fe3ea024","tid":1850851,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:58:16.000Z","msg":"但地震海嘯同決堤係天災嘛"},{"pid":"d60e5543aa1013b3e2ffa0377ecdd3d3fdec29da","tid":1850851,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:00:50.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"e4176a9c14dbb269268ad8cdbb65e036688db7b6","tid":1850851,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已